{"tid":1214522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有個明白事理既老豆真係好感動","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:52:44.000Z","uid":236178,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"34d135ef4ce1675bb35edfc9608de4b9a74b9812","tid":1214522,"uid":236178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"以下內容全部都係發夢見到<br />\n<br />\n本來同佢地唔係好傾呢D野<br />\n今日一訓醒佢就問我琴日去左邊 做咩唔番屋企<br />\n我話無去邊 去左朋友屋企玩<br />\n佢一聽我把聲沙鳩曬就問我係咪去左示威 問我有無比人打 同埋有無跟住衝<br />\n<br />\n我答佢有去，有衝立法會<br />\n之後佢竟然話：屌d o靚仔真係on撚99咁 （我果下已經想同佢開波屌過）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得個勇字，無架餐點夠人打呀 起碼都保護自己呀<br />\n點會咁撚蝕底嫁 <br />\n仲叫我衝唔緊要呀，一定一定要保護自己<br />\n唔好蝕底比班死黑警 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最起碼，我番到屋企唔洗再同人抗爭<br />\n我番到屋企睇直播，有人同我一齊屌警犬"},{"pid":"1395ede60f3d37346c4b7e0c16bd0d076d0f4900","tid":1214522,"uid":81569,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"我個friend屋企先搞笑<br />\n老豆老母黃絲<br />\n佢同佢細佬大學畢業 但藍絲<br />\n算唔算極端例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62860913aac4c45b1f33e7560ed9f16f542a56c","tid":1214522,"uid":50123,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"1395ede60f3d37346c4b7e0c16bd0d076d0f4900","tid":1214522,"uid":81569,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"我個friend屋企先搞笑<br />\n老豆老母黃絲<br />\n佢同佢細佬大學畢業 但藍絲<br />\n算唔算極端例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:39:49.000Z","msg":"咁你都同佢fd到.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1492b697089442a9994fd89acc3db3eaefdcc40","tid":1214522,"uid":18395,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score"